Package de.htw.ai.loz.gpan.lpan.transform

Interface FrameToPacket

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PacketComposer
    public interface FrameToPacket
    Transforms a data unit from IEEE 802.15.4 format to IPv6 format using 6lowPAN adaptation specifications. Functionality contains:
    • Validation
    • Storing of fragments
    • Composing of fragments
    • Decompression of the composed data unit
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Miles Lorenz

                                DataFrame fragmentWrapper)
        Validates, stores and defragments if needed, and decompresses the given data unit.
        Parameters:
        macUrl - The key identifying the user.
        fragmentWrapper - The possibly fragmented and compressed data unit.
        Returns:
